These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, golf, badminton, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
2. the person drinking soy-milk is not the person who's sport is rugby##6
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | sprite    | 7up    | hot-chocolate |
| Sport      | snowboarding | rugby | badminton | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, almond-milk, coffee
There 4 different types of food: pear, asparagus, kiwi, cherry
1. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
3. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
4. the person drinking fanta is not the person eating asparagus##6
5. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | fanta  | almond-milk    | 7up | coffee    |
| Food       | cherry | asparagus | kiwi  | pear |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, milk, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, writer, scientist, paramedic
1. the person drinking almond-milk is not the engineer##6
2. the writer is not the person drinking milk##6
3. the scientist is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
4. the writer is the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the writer##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
7. the engineer is on the far left or far right##3
8. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk       | 7up  | soy-milk  | milk |
| Job        | scientist | paramedic | writer | engineer  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, hamster, frog, goat
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, taxi, boat, snowmobile
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
3. the person driving the snowmobile is not the owner of the hamster##6
4. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
5. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
6. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | hamster | frog | goat     | pony |
| Transport   | taxi     | boat    | motorbike | snowmobile    |

