.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, water, coffee
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, helicopter, scooter, ship
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
4. the person drinking juice is not the person driving the ship##6
5. the person driving the van is not the person drinking sprite##6
6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | sprite        | coffee | water | juice |
| Transport   | ship | van | helicopter     | scooter   |

