.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, animation, martial-arts, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, argentine, brazilian
1. the american is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is not the dutch##6
3. the american is on the far right##1
4. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the american##5
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
8. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
9. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | martial-arts    | documentary  | scientific   |
| Nationality   | argentine  | brazilian | dutch | american |

