.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, martial-arts, satire, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, techno, salsa, blues
1. the fan salsa is on the left or right of the fan rock##3
2. the fan salsa is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
3. the person watching superhero movies is the fan techno##1
4. the fan rock is on the left or right of the fan blues##3
5. the fan salsa is on the far left##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is the fan rock##1
7. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the fan rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | martial-arts     | satire | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | rock | blues      | techno         |

