.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, juice, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, security-guard, fisherman, designer
1. the pilot is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the designer is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
3. the designer is on the right of the security-guard##1
4. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
5. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
6. the pilot is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
8. the person drinking lemonade is not the designer##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | hot-chocolate        | juice      | fanta          |
| Job        | pilot | security-guard | designer | fisherman |

