2. the person driving the jet-ski is not the project-manager##6
3. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
4. the person driving the scooter is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the scooter is the librarian##1
7. the videographer is not the person driving the scooter##6
8. the engineer is somewhere to the right of the project-manager##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | videographer  | librarian | project-manager    | engineer |
| Transport   | jet-ski | scooter | ship | taxi  |

