.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard, goat, guinea-pig
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, cycling, sailing, handball
1. the person who's sport is rugby is not the owner of the mouse##6
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the owner of the goat is not the person who's sport is handball##6
6. the person who's sport is cycling is not the owner of the lizard##6
7. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the goat is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | goat | mouse        | guinea-pig  | lizard     |
| Sport   | rugby     | handball | cycling | sailing |

