.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, sudoku, baking, cooking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, d&b, country, hip-hop
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
2. the fan d&b is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
3. the fan country is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the fan hip-hop and the person who's hobby is baking##2
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the fan d&b is between the fan rock and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | baking | sudoku    | magic-tricks | cooking |
| Music-Genre   | rock         | d&b | hip-hop   | country     |

