.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, tomato, eggplant, watermelon
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, helicopter, subway
1. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
2. the person eating watermelon is not the person driving the airplane##6
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person eating watermelon##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is not the person eating watermelon##6
6. the person eating tomato is not the person driving the airplane##6
7. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
8. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | pineapple  | eggplant | tomato | watermelon |
| Transport   | helicopter | airplane     | subway     | motorbike    |

