.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, cucumber, lemon, apricot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, satire, disaster, superhero
1. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person eating cucumber##5
2. the person eating cucumber is not the person watching satire movies##6
3. the person eating tomato is the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
5. the person eating tomato is between the person eating cucumber and the person watching animation movies##2
6. the person eating cucumber is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | apricot | cucumber      | tomato | lemon   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | disaster | superhero   | animation |

