The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, comedy, zombie, horror
1. the person watching zombie movies is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
2. the person watching zombie movies is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person watching horror movies is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | soy-milk       | juice | mirinda     | iced-tea     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | zombie       | horror | comedy |

