.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, puzzles, filmmaking, rock-climbing
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, ferret, hamster, hedgehog
1. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
8. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | puzzles | filmmaking | hiking | rock-climbing |
| Pet     | hamster  | ferret      | guinea-pig  | hedgehog       |

