The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, subway, helicopter, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the ship is not the person drinking sprite##6
5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
6. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | sprite | fanta | 7up      | tea   |
| Transport   | trike  | subway   | helicopter | ship |

 